name: Pura Luhur Jagasatru
address: J39Q+695, Wongaya Gede, Penebel, Tabanan Regency, Bali 82152, Indonesia
review 1: it is really a beautiful,quite and peaceful temple.need to walk around 30 minutes to get to the temple,wet and a bit slippery road and at the end there are some stair (200 staircases) to to climb to get to main temple,the scenery of the valley around the temple is amazing...
review 2: It was a awesome experience that i could pray at that temple. Covered by sacred forest in batukaru hills.
